sections.Trivia:
- The Cheetah Delivery Service is featured in a flashback in this case.
- The name of the suspects come from cat breeds[2]:
Mutsumi Shagawa (舎川 睦実) comes from siamese cats (シャム猫 ,shamu-neko?);
Teishi Masuko (益子 貞司) comes from scottish folds (スコティッシュフォールド ,sukotisshufōrudo?);
Shugo Amesawa (雨澤 章吾) comes from american shorthairs (アメリカンショートヘア ,amerikanshōtohea?);
Furuyo Tsuyuguchi (露口 降代) comes from russian blues (ロシアンブルー ,roshianburū?);
Mari Aso (麻生 茉莉) comes from somali cats (ソマリ猫 ,somari-neko?);
Rinpei Urushiya (漆屋 倫平) comes from persian cats (ぺルシャ猫 ,perusha-neko?).
